flowchart TD
    subgraph Backup
        DB[(Live Database)] --> FullBackup[Full Backup\npg_basebackup / xtrabackup]
        DB --> WALArchive[Continuous WAL Archiving]
        FullBackup --> Storage[(Backup Storage\nS3 / GCS / disk)]
        WALArchive --> Storage
        Storage --> Verify[Verify backup integrity]
        Verify --> RetentionPolicy[Apply retention policy\ndelete old backups]
    end

    subgraph Restore
        RecoveryTarget[Define recovery target\ntimestamp or latest] --> FindFullBackup[Locate latest full backup]
        FindFullBackup --> RestoreFull[Restore full backup\nto target server]
        RestoreFull --> ApplyWAL[Apply WAL segments\nup to recovery point]
        ApplyWAL --> ConsistencyCheck{Consistency\ncheck passed?}
        ConsistencyCheck -->|Yes| OpenDB[Open database to traffic]
        ConsistencyCheck -->|No| InspectCorruption[Inspect corruption\ntry earlier recovery point]
    end

    Storage --> RecoveryTarget
